# =============================================================
# HOMEBOX — ENVIRONMENT VARIABLES
# =============================================================
# Copy this file to .env and fill in your values
# NEVER commit the .env file — only .env.example
# Shared variables (ROOT_DOMAIN, DOCKER_DATA_PATH, TZ)
# come from root .env
#
# Homebox has no required secrets beyond what root .env
# provides. Configuration is handled via environment
# variables in docker-compose.yml.
#
# First login: create an account at https://homebox.eirdom.homes
# The first registered account becomes the admin.
# Create your account before sharing with family.
# =============================================================
